  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6610043">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6610043/" class="title-link">一本不错的东线的参考资料</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6610043"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/80856381/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/80856381/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">[已注销]</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-03-28"
      class="main-meta">2014-03-28 19:00:35</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6610043_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  首先，我要说明，我对二战东线战场的了解比较有限。这是我完整看完的第一部专门讲述苏德战争的战史书籍。所以可能有很多错误的看法，希望大家谅解。 首先，我要承认，作者的文笔非常棒。作者用流畅的文笔描写了东线战场的形形色色的人物，上到元帅将军，下到普通士兵，构成了一...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6610043/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">10有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6610043_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6610043_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



