  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8059983/" class="title-link">补充之书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8059983"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/humajun/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3079727-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/humajun/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">胡麻君</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-08-26"
      class="main-meta">2016-08-26 00:01:51</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8059983_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  看完了比弗的《保卫斯大林格勒》，为了进一步扩充和加深印象而看的书，也许是读得目的性太强了，所以自感能吸引并运用的东西并没有那么多，但可读性很强。。。五星赏给小小冰人，挺喜欢他的译文的，哈哈，不知他本人的行文风格是怎么样的，译了那么多二战的书，想来他应该是个...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
